title: Molitor - #lonelypeople_Music (2014)
description:
Brand new EP from Toronto, Canada Indie/Rock artist Molitor. Really artistic combination of rock, hip-hop, EDM, disco. This is the 2nd release from Molitor. Molitor is 21 years old and currently working on debut full-length album. According to his website the album will be with the same people as Imagine Dragons and The Killers so he's definitely someone to look out for.

CD Quality - 320kbps
